Requirement for the rpg, Gameplay Requirements:
- Player has the ability to click on button called "Enter Dungeon" to enter Dungeon.
- Clicking "Enter Dungeon" initiates a battle against a random enemy.
- Battle is turn-based.
- Player alwaus takes the first turn.
- Current Available actions are:
1. Attack
2. Flee
- When the player clicks/enters attack, the enemy loses said HP based on current player attack attribute.
- If enemy survives, enemy attacks & player loses HP based on the enemy attack stat.
- If enemy dies, player gains random gold & EXP, and another enemy can spawn.
- If player runs, the dungeon session ends & returns back to main room.
- If player is defeated, the dungeon session ends, the player loses 30% currently held gold.

